mg src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n反對侵侵既人多數都係咁既質素 唔意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實侵都係講一套做一套既姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有時係美國根本無人造呢樣野，所以川普係錯唔曬。"},{"pid":"2fa184d006e04e5bf7e8776c17c5846cccefe547","tid":125760,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T16:30:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>波音好多件都係日本造<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似話787有三分一都係日本造？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n777/787 個中段，仲有787轉左用鋰電，又係三洋(松下)"},{"pid":"fb1f51acb14e55917fbcdf18b35a849161d6541c","tid":125760,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T16:33:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>波音好多件都係日本造<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以唔難理解點解ANA/JAL死都要訂787<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec957c5de926c5c74370d519653a494fdeaae9ef","tid":125760,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T16:35:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>波音好多件都係日本造<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以唔難理解點解ANA/JAL死都要訂787<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁iPhone 有15%利潤係日本公司 ， 唔通又係咁全民iPhone 咩"},{"pid":"98b4ce41b0c1f94fc9ae21e71eb08b111417f20f","tid":125760,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T16:38:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>波音好多件都係日本造<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以唔難理解點解ANA/JAL死都要訂787<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁iPhone 有15%利潤係日本公司 ， 唔通又係咁全民iPhone 咩</blockquote><br />\niphone係日本市佔率都有6成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"830261dd7d8b0a8ad2000e5aeed91a5abe0a163e","tid":125760,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T16:41:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>波音好多件都係日本造<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以唔難理解點解ANA/JAL死都要訂787<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁iPhone 有15%利潤係日本公司 ， 唔通又係咁全民iPhone 咩</blockquote><br />\niphone係日本市佔率都有6成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n淨計智能機九成咁滯，但日本功能機都好智能下，所以佢地仲有人出摺機。"},{"pid":"5c0f6a3c7829b68a02e5098bb593a73da81fdd7b","tid":125760,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T16:43:04.000Z","msg":"自己做晒唔洗做生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088b82cac5a811939afa0899e31e95f1476df270","tid":125760,"uid":34098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T18:33:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本好多所謂新投資係一早定好既計劃黎，俾面侵侵再扮野announce多次姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇日本產經新聞都講過類似，話美國大企業對外話支持make America great again，決定投資幾億美金起廠房。<br />\n<br />\n但一個產房投資講緊要幾十億美元(唔係大陸山寨廠)，根本作大又或者擴建去交差。"}]}